title: Justin Timberlake - What Goes Around (Comes Around) Music Video
description:
What Goes Around - Justin Timberlake (Director&#039;s Cut)

THIS IS THE DIRECTOR&#039;S CUT VERSION. IT IS OVER NINE MINUTES LONG. 

--------------------------------------------

What Goes Around...Comes Around" is the third single from Justin Timberlake&#039;s second solo album FutureSex/LoveSounds (2006). It became Timberlake&#039;s third number one single in the Billboard Hot 100, and also the third consecutive number one single of his sophomore album.

--------------------------------------------

The music video for "What Goes Around...Comes Around" has been described as an "epic video" or a short film since the director&#039;s cut duration exceeds nine minutes and the beginning even features credits similar to a film. The video was directed by Samuel Bayer with dialogue written by Alpha Dog writer and director Nick Cassavetes. This is Timberlake&#039;s first video with explicit language. The video stars Timberlake as well as Scarlett Johansson and Alpha Dog co-star Shawn Hatosy. It also features the interlude ("Comes Around") to the song.

--------------------------------------------
